      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-dat-dsp           not  = zero
                     go to acc-dat-dsp-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-dat-dsp-600
           else      go to acc-dat-dsp-100.
       acc-dat-dsp-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
